@startuml seq-15-ai-chat
' 序列图15：AI文化导师对话
title AI 文化导师对话序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "chat.js" as Front
participant "ChatController" as Ctrl
participant "ChatService" as Svc
participant "application.yml" as Config
participant "DeepSeek API" as API

User -> Front: 输入问题"什么是燕尾榫?"
Front -> Ctrl: POST /api/chat/query(userId,question)
Ctrl -> Svc: query(userId,question)
Svc -> Config: 读取deepseek.api-key
Config --> Svc: apiKey(或环境变量DEEPSEEK_API_KEY)
Svc -> API: HTTP POST api.deepseek.com/chat/completions
API -> API: 大模型推理
API --> Svc: {choices:[{message:{content:"..."}}]}
Svc --> Ctrl: AI回复文本
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, data:reply}
Front --> User: 渲染AI回复气泡

@enduml
